{"tid":1373314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[727元朗整合] 整合左5單要推出國際、要追究嘅野","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:08:58.000Z","uid":131125,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa310f1582bcc0d40eddfa42f56bb7ff9dc067b5","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑狗同政府唔好以為好似上個禮拜咁整多兩樣野出黎<br />\n傳媒消化唔切啲消息就亂鳩咁黎可以再有用</span></span><br />\n呢度5樣單單都好撚嚴重可以揚威國際<br />\n唔好俾佢地走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.中聯辦新界副部長葉虎疑勾結黑幫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372823</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.速龍狗無啦啦入西鐵站內追打民眾</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372960</a><br />\n平民都打...流曬血...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372896</a><br />\n黑警入西鐵站亂棍打人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373047</a><br />\n市民於西鐵站內被速龍亂棍打致昏迷<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.直接攻擊記者同社工</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372691</a><br />\n如果無頭盔 個記者已經俾人爆頭死撚咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372690</a><br />\n【痴撚線】《癲狗日報》記者被催淚彈打中<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=480131086095802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D480131086095802&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3v1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=58e4d514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=480131086095802</a><br />\n19:44 27Jul2019 元朗. 有一名社工畀防暴隊拉，手持社工牌，救傷車 送去醫院。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.民居發射催淚彈、催淚彈射左上老人院</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372149</a><br />\n黑警攻擊老人院！！唔可以再比第二單野淡化！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5.催淚彈射左上西鐵鐵路軌</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1372149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1372149</a><br />\n黑警攻擊老人院！！唔可以再比第二單野淡化！！"},{"pid":"6143a230c14d0844b1de68555f7cf07ccb18a6c2","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味係咪以為次次整左幾單野出黎就會cover到其他醜聞<br />\n呢5單單單都咁撚嚴重全部都要推出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb9c1acf2ae947fafbf26ab3fafb22420ab30be","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"da2db9f2948d07f77c969e242add753fbd1667a6","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0fa671cfaf3b918ddf031a85e439af06b59c1bf4","tid":1373314,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"係時候成立民間防衛隊做返警察應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多證據都證明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警察=黑社會</span></span>，依家嘅警察已經失去合法性<br />\n<br />\n首先可以由集體唔交稅開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7XMWCx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7XMWCx.png&h=73fa9ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceb3eb07d6db5259cb55f717d15927e7f5945982","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c3e3c85fd7d0b265951d5e31abb9b8415c451e","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"次次亂到閪就以為可以魚目混珠?<br />\n食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114b862472470eae07860e8f8849a891277fd0a9","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b717c0602c7b30acd54974845fb08da3dd84f8a7","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36791e61debadfdd952aec93c26f54dad25fa539","tid":1373314,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5a2b223fd6bb1cffd467684fdabee132ab9d85","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"推到文宣接手繼續煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92313d7422814df8539bbaa3329e8bda064741e0","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a20641b00e02a038ddca771f52174bc5fc1ec29e","tid":1373314,"uid":131125,"like":0